reviewText: Very enjoyable and genuine! I'd highly recommend it, and I'm a tough critic too!
Well acted, written, and directed! Very relatable and enjoyable! :)

A great movie that captured the elation and pain of first love. This film posses the innocence and authenticity that is missing from big budget Hollywood films. Heart warming and fun, you have to watch this flick.
Beautiful movie! Kept me hooked and very well written. You can really tell it came from pure honest emotions. Great on all fronts!

This movie embodies real emotion of the fragile ego and embraces the comradery of friendship. Veteran actors Stephen Tobolowsky  & Clint Howard add a special touch to the ensemble cast of fresh-faced, younger actors.  The main character of Ben (Ben Solenberger) draws you into his life and transports your feelings  of consciousness to many levels.  No matter who you are this movie relates to all of usin one way or another.  Worth a watch!
